{"tid":821460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹襲港】打風跑三百級樓梯送外賣 外賣叔：我咩風都見過晒","createTime":"2018-09-16T03:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T06:31:20.000Z","uid":66943,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e09b75bbd32e6fa3f0120c492f58239836317b10","tid":821460,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180916/58682684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58682684&d=At%2FmxAuYDGgbNgvGzD8Mh7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=202a50f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58682684&h=1276b4e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180916/58682684</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n颱風山竹殺到香港，躲在家中，你會否叫外賣？72歲的譚炳文（文哥）在中上環送外賣近八年，打風也不手軟：「不怕的，我咩風都見過晒！」以前文哥做燒臘師傅，早慣了三號風都要送外賣，現在他於「上環食堂茶餐廳」工作，就愛用擔挑送外賣。「40多個飯盒都是這樣挑去，用四個紅白藍袋載好。」風大雨大時，他也沒甚麼特別裝備：「穿雨褸和水鞋囉。橫風橫雨打過來，避也避不到，一定會濕身！試過三號風送去（香港中華基督教）青年會，去樓梯街，跑二三百級樓梯，都是這樣挑上去。我們要準時送給客人嘛，飯盒放久了便不好吃。」其實茶餐廳老闆陳澤明（明哥）擔心員工安全，八號風球不開舖，文哥反而說：「不怕！如果老闆開工，我照來！看着風怎樣吹便怎樣行囉，有次三號風都照去國金（國際金融中心）。」老闆明哥笑說：「通常客人會跟文哥說聲辛苦了，平日好天不會說的。如果認真大風，我都不想派他出去。若伙記有甚麼意外，自己都不好過啦！對不對？」"},{"pid":"10fad43eafdd1895d36fbacbc1095d20626b0e9c","tid":821460,"uid":114154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>三號風</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890e44575a7c3dae0155667ae57e0765da0973fb","tid":821460,"uid":107671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"新聞👍🏻"},{"pid":"a6bf86e9f959b93b655d3cd1b2461ceaf3f424e5","tid":821460,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"譚炳文轉左行咩"},{"pid":"b14bfebb1fbc9bdf17b4504c43b7ec0ea7e7be93","tid":821460,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"唔係做緊配音？"},{"pid":"f0e6109d14947cc212b26bb67e1624d017e3d061","tid":821460,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"當年相戀意中人"},{"pid":"6b5415dc2304aab4b655b37b414fc44753ff1ec6","tid":821460,"uid":173695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0e6109d14947cc212b26bb67e1624d017e3d061","tid":821460,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"當年相戀意中人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:26:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家性情近</span>"},{"pid":"b94adb2e885aff5af95a7179166c745fb5618d92","tid":821460,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"典型廢老<br />\n三號就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de7e0c88d1acbbf35b83d15b320db99fa826215","tid":821460,"uid":108090,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:33:58.000Z","msg":"奴性重反而變咗吹噓嘅資本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c0b8356d2e236fcf9bb3e0dbb52984c3298423","tid":821460,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6bf86e9f959b93b655d3cd1b2461ceaf3f424e5","tid":821460,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"譚炳文轉左行咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d71a3295a6847b4475815ede2ca5894e25132b","tid":821460,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"